# This script is used to test UW/HMMPHYSICAL layer
# There are 3 nodes placed in line that can transmit each other 
# packets with a CBR (Constant Bit Rate) Application Module
#
# To modem each directed links between two nodes with a 2 state HMM
# use the MCLINK class, to have a 3 state model use MCLINK/EXTENDED

#
#
# Author: Antonio Montanari
# Version: 1.1.0
#
# NOTE: tcl sample tested on WSL2 over Win10, 64 bits OS
#
# Stack of the nodes
#   +------------------------------+
#   |  7. UW/CBR                   |
#   +------------------------------+
#   |  6. UW/UDP                   |
#   +------------------------------+
#   |  5. UW/STATICROUTING         |
#   +------------------------------+
#   |  4. UW/IP                    |
#   +------------------------------+
#   |  3. UW/MLL                   |
#   +------------------------------+
#   |  2. UW/TDMA                  |
#   +------------------------------+
#   |  1. UW/HMMPHYSICAL  |
#   +------------------------------+
#             |         |    
#   +------------------------------+
#   |    UnderwaterChannel         |
#   +------------------------------+

